title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Organic Chemicals
description: Imports of Intra EU - Organic Chemicals in the United Kingdom decreased to 371.75 GBP Million in September from 745.37 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Organic Chemicals in the United Kingdom averaged 400.36 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 842.21 GBP Million in November of 2011 and a record low of 0.50 GBP Million in March of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Organic Chemicals.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
